nodes.title: Lora and news on next version Lora Saving & Strength Scheduling
widgets_values:
This is the LoRA I am using for this demo is:

https://civitai.com/models/1241174/zitil-original-character-glara-h?modelVersionId=2495412

My upcoming V2 of this node pack supports saving your edited Loras. It goes out all been well on Comfy Manager/Github on Dec 27th.  

There is a beta avalable now on my BuyMeACoffee page which has the Saving and Strength Scheduling Features. The beta works great with Z-image. Currently trying to sort Chroma before the 27th.

See the video above for a link to the Beta in the description if you want to play with saving your edited LoRAs early.

nodes.title: TEST PROMPT
widgets_values: A close-up portrait of GlaraH riding a horse in the middle of a storm. A tornado is behind them ripping apart a barn. They are running towards the viewer, devastation behind them. Timing is late evening. The sky is full of dark thunder clouds. Location is mid western farmland in the USA. Shot on a 200mm zoom lens.
